## Vercel AI SDK 集成

### 安装

```bash
npm i workers-ai-provider
```

### 文本生成

```typescript
import { createWorkersAI } from "workers-ai-provider";
import { generateText } from "ai";

const workersai = createWorkersAI({ binding: env.AI });
const result = await generateText({
  model: workersai("@cf/meta/llama-3.1-8b-instruct"),
  prompt: "Write a 50-word essay about hello world.",
});
return new Response(result.text);
```

### 流式生成

```typescript
import { createWorkersAI } from "workers-ai-provider";
import { streamText } from "ai";

const result = streamText({
  model: workersai("@cf/meta/llama-2-7b-chat-int8"),
  prompt: "Write a 50-word essay about hello world.",
});
return result.toTextStreamResponse({
  headers: {
    "Content-Type": "text/x-unknown",
    "content-encoding": "identity",
    "transfer-encoding": "chunked",
  },
});
```

### 结构化输出

```typescript
import { createWorkersAI } from "workers-ai-provider";
import { generateObject } from "ai";
import { z } from "zod";

const result = await generateObject({
  model: workersai("@cf/meta/llama-3.1-8b-instruct"),
  prompt: "Generate a Lasagna recipe",
  schema: z.object({
    recipe: z.object({
      ingredients: z.array(z.string()),
      description: z.string(),
    }),
  }),
});
return Response.json(result.object);
```

## REST API

Workers AI 也作为独立 REST API 可用，从任何地方调用：

```bash
curl https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/{account_id}/ai/run/@cf/meta/llama-3.1-8b-instruct \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer {api_token}" \
  -d '{"prompt": "Hello, world"}'
```

## 定价

基于 **Neurons** 计费，**$0.011 / 1,000 Neurons**。

| 套餐 | 免费配额 | 超额价格 |
|------|---------|---------|
| Workers Free | 10,000 Neurons/天 | 需升级 Paid |
| Workers Paid | 10,000 Neurons/天 | $0.011 / 1,000 Neurons |

所有限制在每天 00:00 UTC 重置。

